public interface SubMachine
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'Sub Machine'.

The following features are supported:

  • Machine Modifier
  • Inner Machine
  • External Machine
  • Reflect Machine
  • Variable Machine
  • Machine Body
